### ARCANOS API - GitHub Copilot Compatible HTTP Requests
### Use these examples with GitHub Copilot and REST Client extensions

@baseUrl = https://arcanos-v2-production.up.railway.app
@localUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Health Check - Verify Railway deployment is active
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

### Health Check - Local development
GET {{localUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

### Query Fine-Tuned Model - Main production endpoint
POST {{baseUrl}}/query-finetune
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "What is ARCANOS?",
  "metadata": {
    "source": "github-copilot",
    "timestamp": "{{$datetime iso8601}}"
  }
}

### Query Fine-Tuned Model - Local testing
POST {{localUrl}}/query-finetune
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "What is ARCANOS?",
  "metadata": {
    "source": "github-copilot-local",
    "timestamp": "{{$datetime iso8601}}"
  }
}

### Ask Endpoint - Fallback logic route
POST {{baseUrl}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Test fallback logic",
  "mode": "logic"
}

### Ask Endpoint - Local fallback testing
POST {{localUrl}}/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Test fallback logic",
  "mode": "logic"
}

### API Welcome - General information
GET {{baseUrl}}/api
Content-Type: application/json

### API Welcome - Local
GET {{localUrl}}/api
Content-Type: application/json

### Model Status - Check configured model
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/model-status
Content-Type: application/json

### Model Status - Local
GET {{localUrl}}/api/model-status
Content-Type: application/json

### ARCANOS Router - Intent-based routing
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/arcanos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Test ARCANOS intent routing",
  "domain": "general",
  "useRAG": true,
  "useHRC": true
}

### Memory Storage - Universal Memory Archetype
POST {{baseUrl}}/memory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "test_memory",
  "value": "GitHub Copilot test memory",
  "type": "context",
  "tags": ["github", "copilot", "test"]
}

